{"tid":2155590,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"特首委任林大輝為香港電台顧問委員會主席　 趙應春蘇紹聰加入顧問委員會","createTime":"2020-08-14T01:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T03:05:27.000Z","uid":358308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f904c91fff761a3e2a580102b5e74c4e3e5b25","tid":2155590,"uid":358308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:41:36.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥委任林大輝為香港電台顧問委員會主席，任期 9 月 1 日開始，為期兩年。<br />\n<br />\n憲報又公布，林鄭月娥委任趙應春和蘇紹聰為香港電台顧問委員會成員，任期下月開始，為期兩年。<br />\n<br />\n林大輝乃公職王，本身非港台顧問委員會成員，現為香港體育學院主席及香港理工大學校委會主席。<br />\n<br />\n趙應春是資深傳媒人，曾任有線執行董事。蘇紹聰乃律師會前會長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%A7%E8%BC%9D%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E8%B6%99%E6%87%89%E6%98%A5%E8%98%87%E7%B4%B9%E8%81%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25BC%259D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E8%25B6%2599%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2598%25A5%25E8%2598%2587%25E7%25B4%25B9%25E8%2581%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=ede3a386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25BC%259D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E8%25B6%2599%25E6%2587%258